name: Bonmu Hexcrawl Map
description:
This includes the following:

  • Bonmu Island Hexcrawl Map (@Pinewave for the Fog of war map)

    • Highly recommend using the World Explorer module with this, alternatively you can use Fog of War

  • Bonmu Island Hexcrawl Map Markers Journal

Note any related Macros etc. are within the Fists of the Ruby Phoenix: Addons adventure (these are separate so that you don't have to erase the whole map progress if you reimport the adventure)
